import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import Table from '../components/table/Table' import '../components/topnav/topnav.css' //import workerList from '../assets/JsonData/workers-list.json' import { Axios } from 'axios' const workerTableHead = [ 'serial', 'name', 'email', 'phone', 'type', 'location', 'ratings' ] const renderHead = (item, index) => {item} const renderBody = (item, index) => ( {item.serial} {item.name} {item.email} {item.phone} {item.type} {item.location} {item.ratings} ) const Workers = () => { const [ workerList, setWorkerList ] = useState([]) function getWorker(){ Axios.get('http://localhost:5001/api/workers') .then((response) => response.data) .then((data) => { setWorkerList(data) }) .catch(err => console.log("here's an error" + err)) } useEffect(() => { getWorker() }, []) return (

workers

renderHead(item, index)} bodyData={workerList} renderBody={(item, index) => renderBody(item, index)} /> ) } export default Workers
